reviews.review_text:
if it weren't for AI Now I know we are all spoiled.

This is a really good audiance tape and most of us would never  give it a thought.

The sound is clean with a nice audiance reaction to a high energy 85' show.

Its a 4 star because its not a sbd but try it you'll like it I bet.

DAY TRIPPER!! Love this show. Great quality AUD
I wore out 2 cassettes of this show back in the day.

the playing noodling after wheel, I always thought that they were doing the PITB backwards that night, ie, the Jam before the verses. :)
